            </h3>
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Quick messaging support</p>
              <a 
                href="https://wa.me/919876543210" 
                target="_blank"
                class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200"
                style="background-color: #0003ff; hover:background-color: #0002e6;"
